# Component Patterns

## File Organization

```
src/components/
  layout/            # Shell components (LeftNav, TopNav, AppLayout)
  ui/                # Reusable primitives (TrapezoidalTabs, InlineEditField, FileDropOverlay)
  features/
    customer-link/         # CustomerLinkModal, ContractPreview, ExtractedMappedRow, CustomerLinkContent
    contract-processing/   # SectionHeader, LabelValueList, ProductsPricingTable, InvoicePreview, InPageNav, CommentsPanel, GradientSparkle
```

## Imports Order

1. React/external libraries
2. Lucide icons
3. Internal utilities (`cn`, etc.)
4. Assets (images, SVGs)
5. Local components/types

## Styling Conventions

- Use Tailwind utility classes
- Use `cn()` helper for conditional classes
- Avoid inline styles except for dynamic values or SVG gradients

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
className={cn(
  'base-classes here',
  condition && 'conditional-class'
)}

// ❌ BAD
style={{ padding: '16px' }}
```

