## Inline Edit Field Pattern

Click-to-edit fields that show as text, become editable inputs on click:

```tsx
import { InlineEditField, InlineEditSelect, InlineEditCheckbox, InlineEditRadioGroup } from '@/components/ui/InlineEditField'

// Text input - click to edit
<InlineEditField
  label="Email ID"
  value={value}
  onChange={setValue}
  required
  type="email"
  helperText="Optional helper text below"
/>

// Select dropdown
<InlineEditSelect
  label="Language"
  value={value}
  onChange={setValue}
  options={[{ value: 'en', label: 'English' }]}
/>

// Checkbox with helper
<InlineEditCheckbox
  label="Do not sync"
  checked={checked}
  onChange={setChecked}
  helperText="Check to disable syncing"
/>

// Radio group
<InlineEditRadioGroup
  label="Auto-collection"
  value={value}
  onChange={setValue}
  options={[{ value: 'on', label: 'ON' }, { value: 'off', label: 'OFF' }]}
/>
```

